nodes.text: TZ-33 was a T-series tactical droid stationed on Felucia, and was present during the Second Battle of Felucia.

Around 21 BBY, TZ-33 oversaw the droid army during the Second Battle of Felucia when reinforcements arrived in a Separatist ship. He was in charge of General Grievous's droid outpost on Felucia. However, Republic AT-TEs began firing on the outpost, whereupon TZ-33 ordered the gates of the outpost be lowered so that droids could be sent out to investigate. But it turned out to be a trap, and soon, the Jedi and clones stormed the compound and destroyed all the droids present. TZ-33 was also destroyed when Jedi General Anakin Skywalker bisected him diagonally through his torso.
This tactical droid was voiced by Dee Bradley Baker. His voice was unusual compared to other notable tactical droids.
